autojump authors and contributors
=================================

Main Author
-----------
William Ting <wbting1@gmail.com>

Core Contributors
-----------------
- William Ting <wbting1@gmail.com> (original author)
- The autojump community

Notable Contributors
--------------------
- Developers who contributed patches, bug fixes, and improvements
- Shell script maintainers for bash, zsh, fish, tcsh support
- Platform compatibility contributors (Linux, macOS, Windows)
- Documentation writers and translators

How to Contribute
-----------------
1. Fork the repository
2. Create a feature branch
3. Make your changes
4. Write or update tests
5. Submit a pull request

For more information, see the project README and contributing guidelines.
